author: Branch Education
description:
Have you ever wondered what the inside of a computer power supply looked like?  In this video, we open a power supply and explore its different sections.  Specifically, we'll look at the high-voltage input power side and the low-voltage output power side.  
If you're curious as to how computers work, watch the full video -- https://youtu.be/d86ws7mQYIg
title: How do Power Supplies Work? #pcbuild #powersupply #gamingpc
